food

Class Seeds

  • java.lang.Object
    • Game.Item
      • food.Food
        • food.Seeds

  • public class Seeds
extends Food
    Class to create a seeds food object. Inherits methods and attributes from the Food abstract class; thus behaves as a food to be fed to pets. Properties are unique to the seeds object. Seeds objects are created such that for all instances acting as seeds, they can be changed here.
